text: Royal Regatta () is a 1966 Soviet comedy movie directed by Yuri Chulyukin.Объявлена конкурсная программа и состав жюри 25-го ОРКФ «Кинотавр»КОРОЛЕВСКАЯ РЕГАТА It stars Natalya Kustinskaya, Valentin Smirnitskiy, and Aleksandr Gruzinsky. == Actors == * Natalya Kustinskaya as Alyona, a stewardess * Valentin Smirnitskiy as Vasya * Aleksandr Gruzinsky as Sexton * Aleksandr Khanov as Grandfather * Georgiy Kulikov as Nikolai Lvovich 'Niels Bohr' - a coach * Vyacheslav Zakharov as Seva - a coxswain * Aleksandr Potapov as Taras == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1966 movies Category:Soviet comedy movies
title: Royal Regatta
